Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.84,0:22:10.10,5-normal,signs,0,0,0,,{\an4\fs65\fad(670,0)\bord3\c&H21182D&\3c&HDAE7EE&\pos(615,341)}Laporan Kondisi Wilayah Nezrose\NRakyat: Alna, gadis Suku Oni\NKlaus, mantan prajurit Kerajaan yang mengagumi sang pahlawan\N2 ekor Mbeq, makhluk mirip domba\NFasilitas: 2 Yurt / 2 Gudang\NKandang Mbeq / Dapur / Sumur
Dialogue: 10,0:00:01.14,0:00:07.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tuan! Alna! Kalian baik-baik saja?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:07.11,0:00:09.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita disuruh memeriksa keadaan\Nkarena mereka lama tak kembali.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:09.94,0:00:12.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kepala suku kita memang\Nsuka seenaknya sendiri.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:12.16,0:00:15.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi aku juga khawatir sama Alna, sih.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:17.78,0:00:19.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,I-Itu, 'kan...?!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:21.62,0:00:23.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku mau menikah.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:23.28,0:00:25.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku mau menikah denganmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:25.63,0:00:28.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Menikah, menikah.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:28.63,0:00:34.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,- Menikah, menikah denganmu.\N- Alna, tenang dulu.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:06.04,0:02:07.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hei!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:07.48,0:02:10.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tuan Dias berhasil\Nmenumbangkan Earth Dragon!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:13.98,0:02:17.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mengangkut kura-kura raksasa itu\Nberat sekali.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:17.62,0:02:19.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,Waktu kami akhirnya sampai desa,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:19.86,0:02:23.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,matahari sudah tinggi di langit.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:25.75,0:02:28.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sampai seheboh ini, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:28.82,0:02:32.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tak kusangka kau bisa\Nmenumbangkannya sendirian.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:32.98,0:02:34.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Moll.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:34.66,0:02:39.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku mau tukar bahan dari makhluk ini\Nuntuk bikin sumur dan toilet...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:39.42,0:02:40.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kira-kira cukup, tidak, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:40.64,0:02:42.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lebih dari cukup.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:42.40,0:02:46.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Satu kakinya saja sudah cukup untuk\Nbuat sumur dan toilet di seluruh wilayahmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:46.77,0:02:49.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,Semahal itu?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:49.27,0:02:52.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terlalu berharga sampai kami\Ntak sanggup menyimpannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:52.22,0:02:55.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sebagian besar bahannya\Nakan kami kembalikan padamu.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:56.48,0:03:00.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yang bisa kami tawarkan\Nhanya jasa memotong makhluk itu,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:00.82,0:03:08.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,ditambah bahan sumur, toilet, Yurt,\Njuga bahan pangan dan tanaman obat.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:08.76,0:03:11.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kami juga akan mendirikan Yurt untuk gudang.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:11.74,0:03:13.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih banyak bantuannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:13.84,0:03:15.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lalu sisanya,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:15.36,0:03:17.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,mungkin bisa jadi uang hantaran buat Alna.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:19.16,0:03:21.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau kau kasih satu kuku\Natau taringnya saja,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:21.50,0:03:24.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,orang tua gadis itu pasti sangat gembira.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:24.72,0:03:27.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tu-Tunggu sebentar.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:27.02,0:03:29.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Uang hantaran itu maksudnya apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:29.30,0:03:31.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mau tak mau,\Npernikahan ini harus tetap terjadi.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:32.22,0:03:34.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Punya tetangga seorang pembantai naga itu
Dialogue: 10,0:03:34.88,0:03:39.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,menakutkan kalau tidak diikat\Nhubungan yang erat.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:39.76,0:03:40.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selain itu,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:40.99,0:03:44.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,kejantananmu luar biasa\Nsampai bisa membunuh naga,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:44.06,0:03:46.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,jadi kau harus menikah dengan Alna.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:46.12,0:03:50.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau tidak, semua perawan di desa ini\Nakan mengerubutimu, lo.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:51.48,0:03:53.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Waduh, gawat juga kalau begitu.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:53.62,0:03:54.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Betul, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:54.96,0:03:56.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi tenang saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:56.82,0:04:01.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Alna sudah pergi menemui orang tuanya\Nuntuk membahas pernikahan kalian.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:01.18,0:04:02.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:02.30,0:04:05.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pantas saja dari tadi dia tidak kelihatan.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:07.10,0:04:11.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa tidak bisa diselesaikan\Ndengan pertunangan saja?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:11.89,0:04:15.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Suku Oni tidak punya adat pertunangan.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:15.98,0:04:18.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nikah saja dulu.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:18.02,0:04:20.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Soal kapan mau "menyentuhnya",\Nitu terserah kau,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:20.68,0:04:23.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,anggap saja itu jalan tengahnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:25.16,0:04:26.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau hubungan kita makin erat,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:26.94,0:04:31.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,makin mudah juga bagi kami mendukungmu\Njadi penguasa wilayah yang hebat.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:33.48,0:04:35.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku berterima kasih atas perhatian kalian,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:35.94,0:04:37.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,tapi kenapa sampai sejauh ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:38.06,0:04:39.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau kau lengser,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:39.98,0:04:43.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,kami tak tahu lagi\Npenguasa wilayah macam apa yang akan datang.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:44.34,0:04:48.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yang sebelumnya saja\Nsudah idiot, tak berguna pula.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:48.04,0:04:50.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kudengar dia baru saja mati karena sakit.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:52.68,0:04:55.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi, berjuanglah,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:55.31,0:04:56.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,wahai Tuan Penguasa Wilayah.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:57.82,0:05:00.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Alna juga hebat, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:00.22,0:05:02.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Di usia semuda itu, lo.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:02.44,0:05:05.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hei, berapa umur Alna?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:05.20,0:05:07.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia baru genap 15 tahun.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:07.66,0:05:11.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baru saja cukup umur untuk menikah,\Nlangsung memikat pria sehebat Tuan.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:11.58,0:05:14.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benar-benar luar biasa.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:14.86,0:05:16.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Li-Lima belas...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:17.72,0:05:22.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagiku yang berumur 35 tahun,\Nitu sudah seperti anak sendiri.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:23.28,0:05:26.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Di kerajaan,\Npernikahan baru boleh mulai usia 18 tahun.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:26.86,0:05:29.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku akan minta masa pertunangan tiga tahun,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:29.94,0:05:32.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,dan selama itu,\Naku harus jadi penguasa wilayah yang hebat.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:33.42,0:05:36.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku harus mantapkan tekad\Nsebelum saat itu tiba.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:36.64,0:05:39.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sebagai penguasa wilayah,\Nsekaligus sebagai pria.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:39.34,0:05:40.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dias!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:40.71,0:05:42.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Urusannya sudah beres, lo.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:44.76,0:05:46.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Omong-omong...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:46.70,0:05:49.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Besok pagi kau mau sarapan apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:52.52,0:05:54.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terserah Alna saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:54.20,0:05:57.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Begitu, ya.\NKalau begitu, sampai jumpa nanti!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:02.16,0:06:04.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Alna cantik!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:04.02,0:06:05.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selamat!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:05.03,0:06:06.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selamat, ya!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:06.24,0:06:08.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku iri banget kau bisa menikah dengan Alna!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:08.80,0:06:11.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi dia memang jantan luar biasa.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:11.22,0:06:12.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Wajar saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:12.15,0:06:17.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bisa menikah dengan pria sehebat ini\Npasti bikin Alna bahagia, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:17.23,0:06:19.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukan, ini baru pertunangan!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:19.48,0:06:21.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan malu-malu begitu,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:21.20,0:06:22.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tuan Pembantai Naga!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:27.08,0:06:29.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Beberapa waktu berlalu\Nsejak pesta malam itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:29.68,0:06:31.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sumur dan toilet sudah selesai dibuat,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:31.58,0:06:33.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,fondasi kehidupan pun sudah siap.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:35.88,0:06:39.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sip. Untuk buatan pertama,\Nlumayan juga hasilnya...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:40.12,0:06:43.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Supaya rakyat baru yang datang nanti\Ntak perlu tidur di alam terbuka,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:43.66,0:06:46.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,aku harus bisa merakit lebih baik lagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:48.56,0:06:49.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:49.80,0:06:53.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,bagaimana caranya biar ada rakyat\Nyang mau datang ke sini?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:54.64,0:06:55.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dias!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:56.48,0:06:58.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudah waktunya makan siang?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:58.52,0:06:59.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukan.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:59.66,0:07:02.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada reaksi monster di arah utara.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:02.60,0:07:03.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:03.78,0:07:07.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku pasang sihir pendeteksi kehidupan\Ndi padang rumput.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:07.48,0:07:09.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yang ini terdeteksi sihir itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:09.12,0:07:10.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau tahu jumlahnya?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:11.02,0:07:12.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hanya satu.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:12.44,0:07:14.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ukurannya juga tak seberapa,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:14.54,0:07:17.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,tapi sepertinya sedang menuju ke arah kita.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:19.04,0:07:23.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Gawat kalau sumur dan toilet\Nyang susah payah kita bangun sampai rusak.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:23.04,0:07:27.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terlebih lagi, aku tak bisa biarkan\NFrancis dan yang lain ketakutan.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:27.18,0:07:29.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Biar aku saja yang menumbangkannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:29.05,0:07:31.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku ikut juga.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:31.08,0:07:35.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sekecil apa pun ukurannya,\Nkalau lawannya monster, kita harus kompak.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:35.42,0:07:38.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi bagaimana dengan Francis dan yang lain?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:39.14,0:07:41.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sekarang mereka sedang tidur di gubuk, {\menurutku kalo dipake binatang biasanya pake kandang langsung}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:41.06,0:07:45.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,tapi kalau bangun dan tak ada siapa-siapa,\Nmereka pasti menangis.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:45.31,0:07:47.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apalagi Mbeq sudah terbiasa dengan manusia,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:47.26,0:07:51.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,pasti mereka cemas berat\Nkalau tak merasakan kehadiran orang, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:52.10,0:07:53.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Serahkan saja pada mereka, tidak apa-apa.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:59.88,0:08:01.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sepertinya itu Ogre.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:01.64,0:08:02.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benar.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:03.20,0:08:07.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bahan dari makhluk itu baunya menyengat\Nsampai bikin mual,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:07.44,0:08:09.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,jadi percuma saja memburunya...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:09.86,0:08:11.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa boleh buat.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:11.00,0:08:13.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita harus cegah dia mendekat lebih dari ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:20.20,0:08:21.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Gerakannya lincah juga!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:25.18,0:08:26.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dias!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:26.81,0:08:28.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,Biar aku kunci pergerakan kakinya!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:28.57,0:08:30.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dias, kau serang langsung dari depan!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:30.90,0:08:31.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Paham!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:34.92,0:08:36.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sekarang, Dias!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:45.50,0:08:46.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Berhasil.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:47.44,0:08:49.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini semua berkat Alna.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:49.02,0:08:50.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudah kubilang, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:50.20,0:08:52.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lebih baik kita bertarung bersama.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:52.50,0:08:54.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sebab kita ini sepasang suami-istri.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:55.60,0:08:59.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukan, kita baru tunangan, belum menikah...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:59.18,0:09:00.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Darah Ogre...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:00.94,0:09:02.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bau banget.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:02.18,0:09:03.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sana mandi dulu.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:03.66,0:09:06.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak boleh masuk Yurt\Nsebelum baunya hilang.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:07.20,0:09:09.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baik...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:10.96,0:09:12.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudah sore, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:13.26,0:09:14.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Merepotkan juga.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:15.34,0:09:18.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tak disangka baunya sepekat ini\Ndan susah hilang.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:33.68,0:09:36.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kemarin benar-benar sial.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:37.04,0:09:40.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Rakyat tak kunjung datang,\Nmalah monster yang muncul.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:41.12,0:09:43.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,Harus bagaimana, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:43.27,0:09:45.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dias!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:45.38,0:09:46.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada yang hamil, lo!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:46.77,0:09:48.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Be-Benarkah?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:48.58,0:09:50.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya, kita bakal punya anak!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:53.26,0:09:56.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hore!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:57.02,0:09:59.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sayang, sayang, sayang!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:59.52,0:10:01.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kerja bagus, Francoise!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:01.74,0:10:04.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tak disangka secepat ini\Nkita bakal punya anak.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:04.62,0:10:06.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mbeq, Mbeq.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:08.62,0:10:10.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Francis, kau cemburu?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:10.98,0:10:13.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau juga sudah berjuang keras, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:13.36,0:10:15.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sayang, sayang, sayang.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:15.38,0:10:20.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi sebenarnya,\Nkita tak bisa terus-terusan gembira begini.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:21.76,0:10:26.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau ingat yang kuceritakan\Nsoal kecerdasan Mbeq?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:26.39,0:10:30.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya. Mereka paham sepenuhnya bahasa manusia,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:30.98,0:10:34.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,dan memilih jadi hewan ternak\Ndemi hidup dengan aman, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:34.78,0:10:36.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benar.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:36.34,0:10:40.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Karena pintar, mereka sangat peka\Nterhadap rasa takut dan tekanan batin.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:40.54,0:10:43.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apalagi saat sedang hamil.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:43.28,0:10:48.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bahkan ada kasus mereka mati\Nkarena terpojok rasa takut.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:48.74,0:10:51.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Karena itu, sejak hamil sampai melahirkan,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:51.01,0:10:53.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,mereka butuh sosok terkuat\Ndi kelompok mereka.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:53.04,0:10:56.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Artinya, Dias harus\Nterus berada di sisi mereka,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:56.56,0:10:58.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,dan membuat mereka merasa aman.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:58.80,0:11:02.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Untuk itu, kita harus masukkan Francis\Ndan yang lain ke dalam Yurt,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:02.92,0:11:07.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,tapi bagian dalamnya\Npasti kotor dan bau nanti.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:07.64,0:11:11.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada pria yang sangat tak suka\Nhal semacam itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:11.94,0:11:15.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,Saat Mbeq hamil,\Nini sering jadi pemicu pertengkaran.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:17.48,0:11:21.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oalah, cuma itu.\NAku sama sekali tidak keberatan, kok.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:23.32,0:11:27.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Francis dan Francoise\Nadalah keluarga berharga.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:27.50,0:11:30.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Demi anak mereka lahir dengan selamat,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:31.24,0:11:33.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,hal sekecil itu bukan masalah.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:36.12,0:11:40.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tak kusangka kau tak cuma jantan,\Ntapi juga punya sisi lembut begini.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:40.16,0:11:42.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,Suamiku memang hebat!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:42.47,0:11:44.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:44.48,0:11:46.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mbeq!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:46.22,0:11:47.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mbeq!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:47.84,0:11:48.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mbeq.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:48.64,0:11:51.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Francoise dan yang lain ikut senang juga?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:51.48,0:11:54.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,A-Apa maksudmu, Francoise?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:54.08,0:11:55.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku dan Dias kan belum...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:55.32,0:11:56.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mbeq.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:56.56,0:11:58.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hei, Francis! Sopan sedikit!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:58.48,0:12:02.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kami sedang membangun\Nikatan ini pelan-pelan.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:02.36,0:12:06.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Urusan kami berdua...\Njangan ikut campur, ah!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:08.37,0:12:09.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hijau.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:09.68,0:12:11.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada sesuatu yang datang lagi?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:11.96,0:12:13.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:13.36,0:12:15.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Arahnya dari timur.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:15.58,0:12:18.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sensasi ini...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:18.00,0:12:23.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sepertinya manusia, ada kuda juga.\NJumlahnya sekitar sepuluh...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:23.64,0:12:25.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kupikir begitu.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:25.52,0:12:26.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Timur...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:26.98,0:12:31.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu arah menuju ibu kota,\Ntapi tak ada kabar akan ada tamu.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:31.64,0:12:33.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Biar aku yang memeriksanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:33.94,0:12:37.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Alna, tolong bersembunyi bersama Francis\Npakai Sihir Penyembunyian.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:37.82,0:12:40.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mbeq, mbeq!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:40.19,0:12:43.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tenang saja, aku akan segera kembali.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:43.20,0:12:45.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lagi pula, tak mungkin ada\Nyang lebih tangguh daripada naga, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:46.96,0:12:48.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku akan menjaga tempat ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:49.10,0:12:49.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:54.71,0:12:55.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudah terlihat.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:55.71,0:12:58.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada tiga kavaleri dan empat infanteri.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:58.54,0:13:01.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi totalnya sepuluh\Nkalau kuda dan manusia dijumlahkan.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:02.16,0:13:03.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kira-kira mereka kawan atau lawan...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:04.52,0:13:07.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau mereka musuh dan membawa busur panah,\Nbisa merepotkan.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:07.46,0:13:09.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lebih baik kupangkas dulu jaraknya.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:10.58,0:13:11.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tuan Dias!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:11.66,0:13:12.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lama tak berjumpa!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:14.90,0:13:16.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:16.44,0:13:17.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Klaus, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:17.84,0:13:18.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:19.90,0:13:22.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Anda sudah jadi Penguasa Wilayah, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:22.00,0:13:25.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Senang lihat rekan seperjuanganku sukses!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:25.20,0:13:28.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku juga senang\Nlihat kawan lamaku sehat-sehat.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:28.50,0:13:32.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi ada angin apa sampai datang\Nke tempat terpencil ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:32.04,0:13:35.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku cuma diperintahkan\Nuntuk mengawal dan memandu jalan.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:35.74,0:13:36.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yang di sana itu
Dialogue: 10,0:13:36.96,0:13:39.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,katanya ada urusan dengan Tuan Dias.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:41.18,0:13:42.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Orang itu...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:45.52,0:13:46.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Siapa?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:47.26,0:13:49.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bisa antar kami ke wastu Anda?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:49.66,0:13:53.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Semuanya kelelahan\Nsetelah perjalanan setengah bulan lebih.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:55.08,0:13:57.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dibilang wastu, sih...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:03.98,0:14:06.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Untung semua Yurt, selain yang kubangun
Dialogue: 10,0:14:06.24,0:14:10.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,sebagai latihan, sudah kami sembunyikan.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:10.24,0:14:13.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lagi pula,\Naku sudah janji jaga rahasia Suku Oni,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:13.48,0:14:16.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,menjelaskan semuanya akan sangat merepotkan.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:18.38,0:14:20.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ah, lubang...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:20.00,0:14:23.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa itu rusak saat dirakit, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:25.11,0:14:28.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Izinkan aku perkenalkan diri lagi,\NTuan Pahlawan Dias.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:28.02,0:14:30.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Suatu kehormatan bisa bertemu Anda.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:30.52,0:14:34.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku Diane, putri ketiga.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:34.56,0:14:35.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Seorang putri?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:36.18,0:14:38.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa orang sepenting beliau\Nrepot-repot ke sini?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:38.77,0:14:40.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oleh karena itu,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:40.68,0:14:43.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,apa wastu Anda\Nmasih dalam proses pembangunan?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:43.84,0:14:46.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku juga tak lihat ada pelayan di sini.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:46.72,0:14:49.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ah, Diane, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:49.40,0:14:50.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lancang sekali kau!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:50.18,0:14:52.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Berani-beraninya\Npanggil Putri Diane tanpa gelar!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:52.74,0:14:54.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sadar posisimu!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:56.02,0:14:57.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudahlah, mundur.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:59.81,0:15:04.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Diane, di sini tak ada wastu\Nataupun pelayan.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:04.80,0:15:06.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yang ada cuma rumah ini saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:06.92,0:15:09.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mungkin hasilnya jelek,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:09.52,0:15:12.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,tapi ini kurakit sendiri semampuku.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:13.80,0:15:15.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau rakit sendiri?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:15.72,0:15:18.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lalu ke mana para tukang kayunya?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:18.06,0:15:19.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Setahuku, Tuan Dias
Dialogue: 10,0:15:19.98,0:15:25.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,maksudku, sudah menerima hadiah uang besar\Ndan dana awal dari Ayahanda, Yang Mulia Raja.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:25.78,0:15:27.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dana apa maksudmu?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:27.57,0:15:31.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,Satu keping tembaga pun\Naku tak menerimanya, kok.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:31.07,0:15:33.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak mungkin.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:33.16,0:15:37.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangankan uang, aku bahkan dibuang ke sini\Ntanpa air dan makanan.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:37.33,0:15:40.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Awalnya kukira\Naku bakal mati mengenaskan di sini.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:45.24,0:15:49.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lalu, Diane ada urusan apa datang menemuiku?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:51.58,0:15:52.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Perang.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:54.54,0:15:56.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Saat ini, di ibu kota,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:56.12,0:15:58.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,gejolak perang baru sedang memuncak.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:58.97,0:16:02.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Karena itu, aku datang untuk memohon bantuan
Dialogue: 10,0:16:02.84,0:16:06.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,dari sang Pahlawan Penyelamat Negara\Nagar bersedia kirim pasukan.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:06.73,0:16:08.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sebagai imbalannya, kau bisa menikahiku,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:08.73,0:16:13.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,atau Prinessia, atau Miralda di belakangku.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:16.30,0:16:18.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Perang, katanya?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:18.16,0:16:19.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yang benar saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:20.52,0:16:24.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Saat ini, aku tak mungkin bisa\Ntinggalkan sisi Francoise.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:24.83,0:16:28.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terlebih lagi, pernikahan dengan orang\Nyang baru pertama ditemui
Dialogue: 10,0:16:28.02,0:16:30.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,sama sekali bukan imbalan.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:34.32,0:16:36.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maaf saja, Nona Diane.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:36.12,0:16:38.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tak akan ikut berperang lagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:40.42,0:16:42.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kirim pasukan juga tak mungkin.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:42.18,0:16:46.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,Seperti yang kau lihat, boro-boro prajurit,\Nsatu rakyat pun aku tak punya.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:47.44,0:16:50.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa Anda tak mau mempertimbangkan lagi?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:50.08,0:16:51.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Soal imbalan,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:51.32,0:16:51.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,kami...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:51.80,0:16:53.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tak bisa membantu.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:53.46,0:16:55.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau cuma itu urusanmu,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:55.00,0:16:56.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,segera pulang saja, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:56.32,0:16:57.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lancang sekali kau!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:57.74,0:16:59.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dasar rakyat jelata sok sukses!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:59.58,0:17:01.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Berulang kali tak sopan pada Putri Diane,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:01.45,0:17:02.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,takkan kumaafkan!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:02.98,0:17:03.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hei!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:07.10,0:17:07.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,A-Apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:07.88,0:17:10.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ma-Mati rasa...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:10.38,0:17:14.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tadi itu bahkan tak bisa disebut\Nnafsu membunuh.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:14.13,0:17:16.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau tujuannya mengancam,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:16.01,0:17:18.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,caranya kekanak-kanakan sekali.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:19.84,0:17:21.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Urusanmu sudah selesai, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:21.28,0:17:22.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sana cepat pulang.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:22.89,0:17:24.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayo, lebih baik kita pulang saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:24.70,0:17:26.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau membuatnya makin marah,\Nbisa gawat nanti.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:26.98,0:17:28.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:28.11,0:17:31.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maju bersama pun,\Nkita bukan tandingan orang itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:32.36,0:17:34.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau masih mau menantangnya?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:34.57,0:17:37.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Menantang sang Pahlawan Penyelamat Negara?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:52.42,0:17:55.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Duh, alas tanahnya jadi rusak sedikit.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:55.34,0:17:58.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bisa-bisa aku dimarahi Alna nanti.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:00.74,0:18:04.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dias... beraninya dia mengusirku.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:04.60,0:18:07.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lihat saja,\Nsuatu hari akan kubuat dia menyesal!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:12.69,0:18:16.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,Wanita-wanita itu\Nsemuanya berwujud merah, lo.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:17.06,0:18:19.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Satu prajurit berwujud biru kuat,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:19.28,0:18:21.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,sisanya merah dan putih.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:21.30,0:18:23.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Alna, sejak kapan kau di sini?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:23.58,0:18:28.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Francoise mengotot mau dekat Dias\Nsampai menangis.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:28.58,0:18:33.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi kami mengawasi situasinya dari sini\Npakai Sihir Penyembunyian.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:34.24,0:18:36.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maafkan aku, ya, Francoise.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:36.09,0:18:38.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku malah pergi meninggalkanmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:39.66,0:18:41.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Francis juga.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:41.22,0:18:42.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mbeq.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:48.26,0:18:49.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih, ya, Alna.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:52.64,0:18:55.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Omong-omong,\Nkarena wujud wanita-wanita itu merah,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:55.76,0:18:57.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,berarti mereka punya niat jahat pada Alna?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:57.99,0:18:59.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:59.16,0:19:05.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sihir Penilai Jiwa milikku mendeteksi\Nniat jahat pada aku dan Dias.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:05.88,0:19:09.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sebab kita ini sudah jadi keluarga.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:12.18,0:19:13.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Begitu, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:13.68,0:19:15.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau benar.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:16.24,0:19:18.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Prajurit berwujud biru kuat itu
Dialogue: 10,0:19:18.46,0:19:20.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,kemungkinan besar...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:22.26,0:19:23.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Omong-omong, Dias...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:23.94,0:19:26.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Alas tanah yang rusak tadi,\Nsiapa yang akan memperbaikinya?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:26.78,0:19:30.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ah, iya. Maafkan aku.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:44.22,0:19:45.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selamat pagi, Dias.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:46.56,0:19:48.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada pengunjung datang.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:48.25,0:19:52.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Cuma satu manusia,\Nposisinya di sebelah timur.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:52.10,0:19:54.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia tampak berjalan kebingungan\Nke sana-kemari.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:54.63,0:19:57.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa ada pengembara yang tersesat?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:59.88,0:20:02.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mbeq. Mbeq.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:02.88,0:20:04.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau mau ikut juga?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:04.89,0:20:07.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau cuma satu orang, tak masalah.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:07.58,0:20:09.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku juga akan pakai Sihir Penyembunyian.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:09.39,0:20:13.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Soalnya aku tak mau lihat\NFrancoise sedih lagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:15.80,0:20:16.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baiklah.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:26.66,0:20:28.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Rupanya Klaus, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:29.40,0:20:30.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tuan Dias!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:30.66,0:20:34.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tadi aku mau berkunjung ke kediaman Anda,\Ntapi malah tersesat.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:35.79,0:20:38.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukankah kau sudah pulang ke ibu kota?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:38.28,0:20:39.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selain itu...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:39.30,0:20:41.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Zirahmu ke mana?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:41.38,0:20:45.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ah, aku sudah dipecat dari tugas prajurit.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:45.06,0:20:47.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pedang dan zirahku juga disita.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:48.32,0:20:50.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan-jangan ini karena salahku?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:50.88,0:20:52.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Karena aku mengusir gadis-gadis itu...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:52.81,0:20:54.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukan begitu, kok.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:54.76,0:20:59.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau perang pecah lagi,\Norang sepertiku pasti dikirim ke garis depan.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:59.02,0:21:01.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku malas,\Njadi sengaja bikin diriku dipecat.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:01.84,0:21:03.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi begitu, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:03.70,0:21:05.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Malah kebetulan sekali.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:05.36,0:21:06.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada hal yang ingin kulakukan juga.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:07.56,0:21:08.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Begitukah?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:08.64,0:21:10.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lalu, apa yang ingin kau lakukan?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:12.33,0:21:15.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tuan Dias, aku ingin bekerja di tempat Anda!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:15.84,0:21:16.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maukah Anda
Dialogue: 10,0:21:16.83,0:21:18.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,mempekerjakanku sebagai prajurit wilayah?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:20.68,0:21:22.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Klaus adalah
Dialogue: 10,0:21:22.64,0:21:25.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,pria yang bisa kuandalkan
Dialogue: 10,0:21:25.96,0:21:28.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,untuk saling menjaga punggung\Ndi medan perang,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:28.70,0:21:30.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,tanpa pernah memandang rendah statusku\Nyang yatim piatu.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:30.97,0:21:34.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sangat menenangkan\Nkalau dia mau jadi sekutu kita.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:34.22,0:21:35.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Namun...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:35.74,0:21:36.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dias.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:37.18,0:21:38.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak keberatan, kok.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:39.80,0:21:42.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dari tadi dia terus berwujud biru.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:42.48,0:21:45.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau minta pendapatku juga, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:45.61,0:21:47.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih, Dias.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:49.22,0:21:53.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tuan Dias, wanita itu dan makhluk\Nmirip domba tadi datang dari mana?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:53.75,0:21:56.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ceritanya bakal panjang, tapi...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:56.64,0:21:59.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pertama-tama, kau mau ikut denganku, Klaus?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:59.60,0:22:00.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:00.62,0:22:02.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih banyak!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:03.48,0:22:08.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dengan begini, aku berhasil\Nmenambah rakyat baru di wilayahku.
